  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "I keep getting dock connected on my Android, how do I get it off?",
  "response": "When your Android device continuously shows \"Dock Connected,\" it can be quite annoying. Here are some steps you can take to resolve this issue:\n\n### Basic Troubleshooting\n\n1. **Restart Your Device**:\n   - Sometimes a simple restart can resolve temporary glitches. Hold the power button, then select \"Restart\" or \"Power Off and Restart.\"\n\n2. **Check for Moisture or Debris**:\n   - Inspect the charging port for any moisture or debris. Clean it gently with a soft brush or toothpick. Be cautious not to damage the port.\n\n3. **Change Cable and Charger**:\n   - Try using a different charging cable and charger to determine if the issue is with the accessories.\n\n### Software-Based Solutions\n\n4. **Safe Mode**:\n   - Boot your device into safe mode to see if a third-party app is causing the issue.\n     - Hold the power button until the power options appear.\n     - Long press \"Power Off\" until you see the option for Safe Mode, then tap \"OK.\"\n     - If the problem doesn't occur in Safe Mode, uninstall recently installed apps to identify the culprit.\n\n5. **Clear Cache**:\n   - Go to **Settings** > **Storage** > **Cached Data** and clear the cache.\n\n6. **App Preferences Reset**:\n   - Go to **Settings** > **Apps** > **Three Dots (Menu)** > **Reset App Preferences**. Confirm the reset.\n\n### Advanced Troubleshooting\n\n7. **Factory Reset**:\n   - **Warning**: This will erase all data on your device.\n   - Back up your data first.\n   - Go to **Settings** > **System** > **Reset Options** > **Erase All Data (Factory Reset)**.\n\n### If the Issue Persists\n\n8. **Service Center**:\n   - If none of the above steps work, you might need to visit an authorized service center. There could be a hardware issue that requires professional attention.\n\nTrying these steps should help you identify and hopefully resolve the \"Dock Connected\" issue on your Android device. If the problem persists, seeking professional assistance would be the best course of action.",
